{"hash":"fd5e052490ac51bb964c977cba1632aad7f28183","data":{"markdownPage":{"id":"e1060ebab66912c625c3067356759b40","title":"on-prem 설치 설명서","description":"","path":"/tool/on-prem-inst/","timeToRead":1,"content":"<h1 id=\"on-prem-설치-설명서\"><a href=\"#on-prem-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85%EC%84%9C\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>on-prem 설치 설명서</h1>\n<h1 id=\"installing-on-premise-msa-easy\"><a href=\"#installing-on-premise-msa-easy\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Installing on-premise MSA-Easy</h1>\n<h3 id=\"1-clone-helm-charts\"><a href=\"#1-clone-helm-charts\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>1. Clone helm Charts</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">git clone https://github.com/msa-ez/on-prem-helm.git</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"2-create--connect-kubernetes-cluster\"><a href=\"#2-create--connect-kubernetes-cluster\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>2. Create &#x26; Connect Kubernetes Cluster</h3>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"3-helm-chart-기반-msa-easy-설치\"><a href=\"#3-helm-chart-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B0%98-msa-easy-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>3. helm chart 기반 MSA-Easy 설치</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Cluster ip: <code>kubectl cluster-info</code></li>\n<li>Domain: DNS 서비스에서 보유한 도메인 주소 </li>\n<li>\n<p>token: <code>kubectl describe secret default</code></p>\n<h4 id=\"1-yaml-파일-별-수정-필요-내용\"><a href=\"#1-yaml-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EB%B3%84-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94-%EB%82%B4%EC%9A%A9\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>1. yaml 파일 별 수정 필요 내용</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><b>deployment.yaml</b>: Cluster ip, Domain, token</li>\n<li><b>values.yaml</b>: Cluster ip, Domain</li>\n<li><b>2q</b>: Domain  </li>\n<li><b>ingress.yaml</b>: Domain </li>\n<li>\n<p><b>issuer.yaml</b> Domain</p>\n<ul>\n<li>변경 후 <b>issuer.yaml</b> 전체내용 주석 </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"2-helm-install-on-prem-\"><a href=\"#2-helm-install-on-prem-\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>2. helm install on-prem .</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>on-prem install 후 <b>issuer.yaml</b> 주석 제거</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"3-apply-issuer-secretsyaml\"><a href=\"#3-apply-issuer-secretsyaml\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>3. Apply issuer, secrets.yaml</h4>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">kubectl apply -f issuer.yaml, secrets.yaml</code></pre>\n<h4 id=\"4-ingress-nginx-설치\"><a href=\"#4-ingress-nginx-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>4. ingress-nginx 설치</h4>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">  helm upgrade --install ingress-nginx ingress-nginx \\\n    --repo https://kubernetes.github.io/ingress-nginx \\\n    --namespace ingress-nginx --create-namespace</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"4-dns-서비스-도메인-record-생성--설정\"><a href=\"#4-dns-%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4-%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8-record-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1--%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>4. DNS 서비스 도메인 record 생성 &#x26; 설정</h3>\n<h4 id=\"1-create-record\"><a href=\"#1-create-record\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>1. Create Record</h4>\n<p>  <img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65217813/192461326-ad37d114-cc4e-4fb8-8813-f45270e31c7d.png\" alt=\"createRecord1\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>gitlab, kas, minio, registry, *, api, www, file, acebase 각 Record 생성\n<img width=\"1007\" alt=\"onprem_createRecord\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65217813/192455799-0f3300f6-7fd9-4ef6-8665-8b5fbafb9831.png\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"1-edit-recordgitlab-kas-minio-registry\"><a href=\"#1-edit-recordgitlab-kas-minio-registry\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>1. edit record(gitlab, kas, minio, registry)</h4>\n</li>\n<li>등록할 IP: <code>kubectl get ing</code>\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65217813/192466549-3336cd69-9a73-440a-843b-0711822f371d.png\" alt=\"getIngress\"></li>\n<li>\n<p>IP 수정\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65217813/192468220-9a1670b3-9ec3-4ffe-98c7-7dc86c6e1778.png\" alt=\"editIngressRecord\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"2-edit-record-api-www-file-acebase\"><a href=\"#2-edit-record-api-www-file-acebase\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>2. edit record(*, api, www, file, acebase)</h4>\n</li>\n<li>등록할 IP: <code>kubectl get svc -n ingress-nginx</code>/ external-ip </li>\n<li>위와 동일한 방법으로 수정 </li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"5-ide-관련-operator-설치\"><a href=\"#5-ide-%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8-operator-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>5. ide 관련 operator 설치</h3>\n<h4 id=\"1-operator-설치\"><a href=\"#1-operator-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>1. Operator 설치</h4>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">cd ide-operator\nmake deploy IMG=gcr.io/eventstorming-tool/theia-ide-lab:v137</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"6-nfs-설치\"><a href=\"#6-nfs-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>6. NFS 설치</h3>\n<h4 id=\"1-bvaluesyamldiskb-수정클러스터에-연결할-disk-명으로-수정\"><a href=\"#1-bvaluesyamldiskb-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95%ED%81%B4%EB%9F%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%84%B0%EC%97%90-%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0%ED%95%A0-disk-%EB%AA%85%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>1. <b>values.yaml/disk</b> 수정(클러스터에 연결할 disk 명으로 수정)</h4>\n<h4 id=\"2-nfs-설치\"><a href=\"#2-nfs-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>2. nfs 설치</h4>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">cd gcp_helm\nhelm install gcp-msaez .</code></pre>\n<hr>\n","sidebar":"started","next":"","prev":"","headings":[{"depth":1,"value":"on-prem 설치 설명서","anchor":"#on-prem-설치-설명서"},{"depth":